headline: Wealth Manager NorthRock Partners Adds $2.7 Billion Ameriprise Advisor Team
summary: WGG Wealth Partners is a 15-advisor practice based in Roseville, a suburb of Sacramento, that specializes in comprehensive financial planning and offers advice on issues such as tax and estate planning.  “NorthRock’s growth is intentional,” NorthRock CEO Rob Nelson tells Barron’s Advisor.

headline: NorthRock Acquires $2.7B Northern California Team From Ameriprise
summary: NorthRock’s deal with WGG Wealth Partners expands its California presence, as it continues toward its goal of becoming a $100 billion RIA.
